✓ All [TIMING] lines preserved inside #ifdef GENDB_PROFILE guards  
✓ Encoding logic unchanged  
✓ Validation expected to pass (CompactHashTable semantically equivalent to unordered_map)  
✓ Compiled successfully with -O3 -march=native  

The optimization focused on the **dominant bottleneck (orders_hash at 46% of total time)** by replacing the slow map structure with a high-performance open-addressing hash table. This is a **plan-level improvement** (data structure choice) rather than micro-optimization, which yields the highest returns.